        <num>CC 562</num>
        <heading>562.  Usufruct of timberlands</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 562.  Usufruct of timberlands.
When the usufruct includes timberlands, the usufructuary is bound to manage them as a prudent administrator.  The proceeds of timber operations that are derived from proper management of timberlands belong to the usufructuary.</p>
        </content>
